<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:350px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-cn-1331/SCP-CN-1331.png" style="width:350px;" alt="SCP-CN-1331.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:350px;">
<p>SCP-CN-1331顯現為男性及女性時的形象，其Akiva輻射在奇術偵測儀下映顯出來。</p>
